<p><a style="font-size:18px; line-height:22px; height:22px;" href="/shiwenv_0b0581866b5f.aspx"><b>采绿</b></a></p>
<p class="source"><a href="https://www.gushiwen.org/shiwen/default.aspx?cstr=%e5%85%88%e7%a7%a6">先秦</a><span>：</span><a href="/search.aspx?value=%e4%bd%9a%e5%90%8d">佚名</a></p>
<div class="contson" id="contson0b0581866b5f">
<p>终朝采绿，不盈一匊。予发曲局，薄言归沐。</p>
<p>终朝采蓝，不盈一襜。五日为期，六日不詹。</p>
<p>之子于狩，言韔其弓。之子于钓，言纶之绳。</p>
<p>其钓维何？维鲂及鱮。维鲂及鱮，薄言观者。</p>
</div>
